    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the act of assigning and enhancing value. In a heritage management context, valorization is used in the sense of highlighting and promoting aspects of cultural patrimony.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
